    "description": "<p>He dwells in a cave full of smoke and bones, tending his stew pot and stewing. He might venture out to fetch firewood, water, or meat — and when he's out, he might cross paths with a mortal. In his loneliness, he might forget just how poorly things went last time. When you Haggle with Grimstew he wants company, not things.</p>",
